Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷佐尔斯受到MS的攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然毫无警告就发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军部队的MS中据说还有新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯  他们是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PROUD的营救作战还是延期…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（PROUD：联邦殖民卫星）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 更应该提前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事关众多同志的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能失去他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我联系营救部队转达作战变更信息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:15.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(535,357)}{\shad3}{\bord1}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}天使再临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我联邦政府为消灭反政府势力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已派遣政府直属的治安维持部队开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安维持部队将与联邦保安局携手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有效率地进行作战…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才司令部下令将我调往独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻中的A-LAWS 亲眼见证也不失为一次良机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支部队中机密甚多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能探查内情自然求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛内金上校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何要事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  那件事考虑过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必这么快决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(365,367)}拉格朗日4  殖民卫星PROUD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这样 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长进不小嘛 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都来这里半年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我新人了 叫我沙慈·库斯洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是埃迪·宫坂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为内通KATARON的嫌疑者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON(希腊语)：反联邦政府组织(本意为纯真)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫坂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得跟我们一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的新建航空巡洋舰 正转变方向前往拉格朗日4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美的报告没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Seravee Gundam：GN-008 炽天使高达，Virtue的强化机型）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活着 必定会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:25.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(365,367)}{\fs19}殖民卫星PROUD   高重力工业区划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:33.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)}{\pos(365,367)}同区   矿石精炼区域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种高重力下 竟然不用机器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停手  R81
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管闲事 想活命就闭上嘴好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作 R81
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离PROUD 2300
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散布  维持通常浓度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰江中校 据说找到KATARON的舰船了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 先行部队捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并开始跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然准备前往PROUD吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型自动机器人的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部机体随时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始对反政府势力的扫荡作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD第一小队  准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:36.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（AHEAD：先锋，A-LAWS新型机）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD第一小队  准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD 自动机器人搭载集装箱 连接完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机能无异常  ALL GREEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉宁上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机的阿勒威准尉是初阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她感受下战场的氛围就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉宁小队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这里也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂能就此屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在宇宙 总有一天能见到路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来不像当过军人 你也是KATARON的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷进来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点撤退  作战就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我们只接到撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别丢下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Realdo部队 初步行动结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Realdo：原Union旧型机体）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始营救作战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介入第7区的重力系统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始介入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出场了  同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 正上方确认到MS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉嘉中尉 干掉敌方部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒威准尉在原地待机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按定计划进行新型自动机器人的性能实验
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集装箱分离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始启动新型自动机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军用自动机器人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
