Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E探测器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们追求的 才不是这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂也是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 那机影是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那种GN粒子是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动机器人的数量 在减少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 为什么你会是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何事到如今还出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的行径
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来驱逐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam  也不过是5年前的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是AHEAD的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机  掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我们自己上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多战友死于你们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇雪恨!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的时代结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后长出脸来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答 三号机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在打探A-LAWS的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了  刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾迪先生发现Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 果然在PROUD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王小姐的情报好准
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会吃惊的 见到拉塞先生时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样总算有机会试用Exia的太阳炉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PROUD出现了Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须感谢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了他们 才能救出幸存的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能会成为武力介入的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是和我们志同道合的人 席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年不见 气质变化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却几乎毫无改变 和当时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常被人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台Gundam 是天人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是驾驶Gundam的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  5年前的武力介入也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗  因为你们的所为 多少人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人受到伤害 家人和亲戚被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的亲姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为跟天人扯上关系 被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝也是 姐姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她们还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会遭到Gundam的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 我们就更有存在的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种家伙会进A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·阿勒威 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你也有战斗的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹  有人求见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队和新的Gundam发生接触
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还未确认Gundam是否隶属天人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府对此事态…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 终于出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未对自己是处女座如此高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前来迎接索玛·比利斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是第五MS中队所属安德烈·史米卢佐夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候加入A-LAWS的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有回答你的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 不  瑟尔盖·史米卢佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:06.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:11.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:18.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:27.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:31.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:39.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:55.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:22:00.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:07.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:12.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:17.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:28.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:06.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:11.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:18.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:27.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:31.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:39.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:55.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:22:00.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:07.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:10.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:12.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:17.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:28.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没对刹那开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人的话就和你们一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢刹那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不带你来这里的话 你就已被当作反联邦势力KATARON处死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不了解现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所处的世界 用自己的眼睛去确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你把我叫出来的吗
